text: Danielle Nicole Panabaker (born September 19, 1987) is an American actress. She is known for acting in many movies. These include Sky High and Mom at Sixteen. She has also acted on the television series including Shark and The Flash. In 2021, she won a Saturn Award for Best Supporting Actress on Television for her role as Caitlin Snow / Frost in The Flash. Panabaker is the older sister of child actress Kay.
